  "detailed_description": "A tightly designed, precision platformer with a large variety of mechanics and over 100 platforming challenges! Jump, dash and glide your way past spikes to get to the end. Teleport past walls, summon a moving cloud platform to cross gaps, recharge your dashes midair, change form, use many different types of dashes, grapple hook to nearby terrain, Cleverly gain enough height to scale tall obstacles. Use multiple new move sets over seven chapters. For players of all skill levels to enjoy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/72e7ac95bde18edc45683986307846fb.poster.avif?t=1663038328\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/72e7ac95bde18edc45683986307846fb.webm?t=1663038328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/72e7ac95bde18edc45683986307846fb.mp4?t=1663038328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/949b911f91e0bd8f164b06f0c192a0da.poster.avif?t=1663038328\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/949b911f91e0bd8f164b06f0c192a0da.webm?t=1663038328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/949b911f91e0bd8f164b06f0c192a0da.mp4?t=1663038328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2093680/extras/38355cd1e0bef308a7b8bee42edcd86a.poster.avif?t=166303